com.diamonddevgroup.utils

Class Helper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.diamonddevgroup.utils.Helper

  • public class Helper
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class to apply styling in code to any component. This eliminates the need to create multiple UIIDs.

    Multiple styling can be applied through chaining.

    Example:
    new Helper(myLabel).py2().textDanger().textCenter()
